    <item>
      <title>耶伦捍卫监管在加强金融稳定中的作用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/yellen-defends-regulation-role-in-bolstering-financial-stability</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特耶伦为监管在支持金融体系韧性方面发挥的作用进行了辩护，并强调其部门在过去几年中一直致力于确保金融体系稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/yellen-defends-regulation-role-in-bolstering-financial-stability</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纳斯达克将上市业务划分为多个区域以吸引需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nasdaq-divides-listing-business-into-regions-to-capture-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳斯达克公司正在将其上市业务重组为三个区域部门，由高管领导，努力满足地方对首次公开募股 (IPO) 的需求。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/nasdaq-divides-listing-business-into-regions-to-capture-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛策略师称美国大选将考验股市乐观情绪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/goldman-strategists-say-us-election-to-test-optimism-in-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团的策略师表示，美国股市自夏季抛售后有所复苏，但这场关系重大的总统大选可能会扰乱投资者对美国股市的乐观情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/goldman-strategists-say-us-election-to-test-optimism-in-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:23:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德每年向桑坦德银行贷款投资 10 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/blackrock-to-invest-1-billion-a-year-in-banco-santander-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贝莱德公司将每年向桑坦德银行的能源和项目融资资产投资高达 10 亿美元，标志着该基金管理公司今年在基础设施领域的扩张又迈出了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/blackrock-to-invest-1-billion-a-year-in-banco-santander-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 10:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全文：黎巴嫩部长萨拉姆谈停火和经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/in-full-lebanese-minister-salam-on-cease-fire-economy-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[黎巴嫩经济贸易部长阿明·萨拉姆在彭博电视台发表讲话，美国、欧洲和阿拉伯国家等国际大国提议以色列和真主党停火三周，以避免全面战争。萨拉姆还讨论了当前的经济状况，以及确保人民生活必需品的应急计划。萨拉姆接受了彭博社记者 Joumanna Bercetche 的采访。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-09-26/in-full-lebanese-minister-salam-on-cease-fire-economy-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 05:36:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日韩考虑对中国钢铁产品采取反倾销行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/south-korea-opens-dumping-probe-on-stainless-steel-made-in-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在世界范围内对中国廉价钢铁产品的抵制情绪日益高涨的背景下，日本和韩国成为最新对中国钢铁产品采取反倾销措施的国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/south-korea-opens-dumping-probe-on-stainless-steel-made-in-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 05:32:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国誓言支持经济增长，铜价再次攀升至 10,000 美元附近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/base-metals-edge-lower-as-doubts-swirl-over-china-s-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国高层领导人加大刺激经济增长的力度后，铜价回升至每吨 10,000 美元，其他工业金属价格也上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-26/base-metals-edge-lower-as-doubts-swirl-over-china-s-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 26 Sep 2024 03:30:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
